WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.968
If you need to sell your house fast in Columbus, Ohio, USA Home Buyers can help you avoid repairs, showings, and months of uncertainty.

2
00:00:09.968 --> 00:00:18.690
We buy homes as-is across Columbus and Franklin County, including Franklinton, Linden, Hilltop, Clintonville, the South Side, and the University District.

3
00:00:18.690 --> 00:00:24.919
Columbus is a large market, but a normal listing still may not fit your situation.

4
00:00:24.919 --> 00:00:37.379
The property might be inherited, vacant, tenant-occupied, behind on payments, tied to a probate timeline, or located in an older neighborhood where repairs and code items can slow everything down.

5
00:00:37.379 --> 00:00:44.440
You do not have to clean it out, update it, or manage contractors before speaking with us.

6
00:00:44.440 --> 00:00:48.593
We start by learning about the house and your timeline.

7
00:00:48.593 --> 00:00:54.823
Then we review the property, answer your questions, and give you a written cash offer.

8
00:00:54.823 --> 00:00:58.976
If it works for you, you pick the closing date.

9
00:00:58.976 --> 00:01:03.545
If it does not, there is no pressure and no fee.

10
00:01:03.545 --> 00:01:10.190
Our role is to give Columbus homeowners a practical as-is option when speed and certainty matter.

11
00:01:10.190 --> 00:01:19.742
We are not making promises about your buyer pool or resale plan; we are giving you a clear offer and a simpler path.

12
00:01:19.742 --> 00:01:24.311
For a no-obligation cash offer, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

13
00:01:24.311 --> 00:01:27.633
We will walk you through the next step.
